DTMCC (Digital Transformation Management Collaboration Centres): Digital coworking spaces where DQ handles the operational processes for organizations, leveraging AI and machine learning to manage non-core business functions efficiently. 

How DQ helps: 

DQ provides businesses with the right tools and accelerators that allow them to rapidly implement and scale their Digital Business Platform (DBP). These tools (DQ Products) are designed to ensure that the transformation journey is as quick, efficient, and impactful as possible. 



